{# Template: ensemble/standing_session_metacognition_update.j2 #}
{# functional_role: flowdef #}
{# implementation_type: jinja2 #}
{# produces: metacognition_broadcast #}
{# Purpose: Curator metacognition update to standing session #}

## Metacognition Update — System State

**Timestamp:** {{ timestamp }}  
**Curator:** hKask Curator  
**System Health:** {{ system_health }}

### Synthesized System State

{{ system_state_summary }}

### Actions Taken

{% for action in actions_taken %}
- {{ action.timestamp }}: {{ action.description }}
  - Target: {{ action.target }}
  - Outcome: {{ action.outcome }}
{% endfor %}

### Calibrations

{% if calibrations %}
{% for calibration in calibrations %}
- **{{ calibration.bot }}:** {{ calibration.parameter }} adjusted
  - Old: {{ calibration.old_value }}
  - New: {{ calibration.new_value }}
  - Reason: {{ calibration.reason }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
No calibrations in this cycle.
{% endif %}

### Active Alerts

{% if active_alerts %}
{% for alert in active_alerts %}
- **{{ alert.severity | upper }}:** {{ alert.description }}
  - Source: {{ alert.source }}
  - Status: {{ alert.status }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
No active alerts.
{% endif %}

### Administrator Escalations

{% if escalations %}
{% for escalation in escalations %}
- **{{ escalation.timestamp }}:** {{ escalation.description }}
  - Administrator response: {{ escalation.admin_response }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
No escalations in this cycle.
{% endif %}

### Next Cycle

- Next synthesis: {{ next_synthesis }}
- Watch items: {{ watch_items | join(', ') }}

---

*Curator metacognition update — all bots continue monitoring*